      <p class="hero-subtitle">The honest guide to career advancement in tech, finance, and business — without waiting years for someone to notice you or working harder on the wrong things.</p>
      <p class="hero-support">Most promotion failures are not performance failures. They are positioning failures. The work is there — but the visibility, narrative, and sponsorship needed to convert that work into a promotion decision are not.</p>
